        Our Projects
      </h2>
      <h3
        class="text-center font-bold text-blue-950 text-lg lg:text-2xl mb-2 lg:mb-4 2xl:mb-6"
      >
        Discover Our Work
      </h3>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-6 px-4"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center lg:max-w-lg">
          <div>
            <Image
              src={projects3}
              alt=""
              class="md:w-80 md:h-80 object-contain bg-white"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="w-[90%] h-[310px] bg-white p-4 shadow-2xl -mt-10 rounded-2xl grid grid-cols-1 justify-center items-start gap-2 md:gap-3 lg:gap-4"
          >
            <h3 class="text-center font-bold text-primary text-2xl lg:text-3xl">
              On-going Projects
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm xl:text-base font-medium text-neutral-500 mt-4">
              Embark on a journey of innovation and progress as we bring our
              ongoing projects to life. From groundbreaking concepts to
              meticulous execution, witness the evolution of modern architecture
              in real-time. Explore our ongoing projects and be part of the
              journey towards a brighter future.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 md:mt-0 py-2 justify-self-end">
              <a
                href="/ongoing-projects"
                class="bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_right,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-sky-500 to-indigo-900 rounded-lg border-2 border-indigo-900 w-fit text-white text-center font-bold p-4 px-6 shadow-2xl scale-100 transition-all hover:scale-105"
